WEBVTT

00:03.209 --> 00:05.783
Wow. It is such a cute bird!

00:06.066 --> 00:07.572
Do you want to touch it?

00:08.866 --> 00:12.169
No way. I'm afraid of birds.

00:14.527 --> 00:17.057
You have a such a nice bike.

00:18.147 --> 00:22.580
Thanks. I saved money for six months to buy this bike.

00:23.125 --> 00:26.015
If you want, you can also buy this one.

00:27.172 --> 00:31.161
No, I can't. I'm afraid to spend all my money.

00:33.512 --> 00:35.851
It is such a beautiful sea.

00:37.161 --> 00:40.737
Let's jump into the sea and enjoy swimming.

00:41.717 --> 00:46.001
No, I can't. I'm afraid of swimming in this deep water.

